[{"id":"page_0362-b001","page_key":362,"order":1,"type":"equation","source":"deepseek","confidence":"high","text":"\\begin{align*}\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}&\\mathbf{z}_{t}+\\frac{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t-1}}\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\mathbf{x}\\\\&=\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}&\\mathbf{z}_{t}+\\frac{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t-1}}\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\left(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}}{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}\\right)\\\\&=\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}&\\mathbf{z}_{t}+\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\left(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}\\right),\\end{align*} \\quad (18.32)"},{"id":"page_0362-b002","page_key":362,"order":2,"type":"exercise","source":"deepseek+paddle","confidence":"medium","text":"Problem 18.9"},{"id":"page_0362-b003","page_key":362,"order":3,"type":"paragraph","source":"deepseek+paddle","confidence":"medium","text":"where we have used the fact that $\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t}}/\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t-1}}=\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}$ between the second and third lines. Simplifying further, we get:"},{"id":"page_0362-b004","page_key":362,"order":4,"type":"equation","source":"deepseek","confidence":"high","text":"\\begin{align*}\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}&\\mathbf{z}_{t}+\\frac{\\sqrt{\\alpha_{t-1}}\\beta_{t}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\mathbf{x}\\\\&=\\left(\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}{1-\\alpha_{t}}+\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{(1-\\alpha_{t})\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\right)\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}\\\\&=\\left(\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})(1-\\beta_{t})}{(1-\\alpha_{t})\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}+\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{(1-\\alpha_{t})\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\right)\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}\\\\&=\\frac{(1-\\alpha_{t-1})(1-\\beta_{t})+\\beta_{t}}{(1-\\alpha_{t})\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}\\\\&=\\frac{1-\\alpha_{t}}{(1-\\alpha_{t})\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}\\\\&=\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{z}_{t}-\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha_{t}}\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon},\\end{align*} \\quad (18.33)"},{"id":"page_0362-b005","page_key":362,"order":5,"type":"exercise","source":"deepseek+paddle","confidence":"medium","text":"Problem 18.10"},{"id":"page_0362-b006","page_key":362,"order":6,"type":"equation","source":"deepseek","confidence":"high","text":"\\begin{aligned}&where we have multiplied the numerator and denominator of the first term by\\sqrt{1-\\beta_{t}}\\\\&between lines two and three, multiplied out the terms,and simplified the numerator in\\\\ \\end{aligned}"},{"id":"page_0362-b007","page_key":362,"order":7,"type":"paragraph","source":"deepseek+paddle","confidence":"medium","text":"Substituting this back into the loss function (equation 18.29), we have:"},{"id":"page_0362-b008","page_key":362,"order":8,"type":"equation","source":"deepseek","confidence":"high","text":"\\epsilon."},{"id":"page_0362-b009","page_key":362,"order":9,"type":"equation","source":"deepseek","confidence":"high","text":"\\begin{align*}L[\\boldsymbol{\\phi}_{1\\ldots T}]\\quad&=\\sum_{i=1}^{I}\\Big(-\\log\\Big[\\mathrm{Norm}_{\\mathbf{x}_{i}}\\left[\\mathbf{f}_{1}[\\mathbf{z}_{i1},\\boldsymbol{\\phi}_{1}],\\sigma_{1}^{2}\\mathbf{I}\\right]\\Big]\\\\&+\\sum_{t=2}^{T}\\frac{1}{2\\sigma_{t}^{2}}\\left\\|\\left(\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{1-\\beta}_{t}}\\mathbf{z}_{it}-\\frac{\\beta_{t}}{\\sqrt{1-\\alpha}_{t}\\sqrt{1-\\beta}_{t}}\\mathbf{\\epsilon}_{it}\\right)-\\mathbf{f}_{t}[\\mathbf{z}_{it},\\boldsymbol{\\phi}_{t}]\\Big\\|^{2}\\right).\\end{align*} \\quad (18.34)"},{"id":"page_0362-b010","pa